    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wishlist now and be the first to play!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.poster.avif?t=1768862859\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.webm?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/5147a5cfdc9f40273a4187d573c253a6.mp4?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to 'Food Delivery Simulator' – Your Ultimate Delivery Experience! </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the shoes of a food courier in the bustling streets of America’s biggest cities. In this first-person, realistic, sandbox RPG game, every delivery is an adventure waiting to unfold.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Earn and Upgrade</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start small and work your way up. Earn money through successful deliveries and invest in motorcycles or cars to enhance your delivery speed and efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/f0f335d89b73481f41ba800981c72555.poster.avif?t=1768862859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/f0f335d89b73481f41ba800981c72555.webm?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/f0f335d89b73481f41ba800981c72555.mp4?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arranging Foods on Tray</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully arrange the food on the tray to boost customer satisfaction. Ensure quality by meticulously placing each item.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/b2c44ce6ce34a94c7b33e41ecd1f9810.poster.avif?t=1768862859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/b2c44ce6ce34a94c7b33e41ecd1f9810.webm?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/b2c44ce6ce34a94c7b33e41ecd1f9810.mp4?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a Vast City</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Roam freely in a massive, highly detailed city. Walk, ride, or drive through diverse neighborhoods, each with its own unique charm and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/d9ac5dbe2c8dbbab6e56f323f48f7602.poster.avif?t=1768862859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/d9ac5dbe2c8dbbab6e56f323f48f7602.webm?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/d9ac5dbe2c8dbbab6e56f323f48f7602.mp4?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build Your Business</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own delivery office. Hire new drivers to expand your business and manage their schedules and routes to maximize profits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/3ddd16bb6a60ea4c63f291f4bcce213f.poster.avif?t=1768862859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/3ddd16bb6a60ea4c63f291f4bcce213f.webm?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/3ddd16bb6a60ea4c63f291f4bcce213f.mp4?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Weather and Time</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the city’s dynamic weather and day-night cycles. Deliver in sunny afternoons, rainy evenings, and everything in between, facing the elements as a true courier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/8d3c312f2f2457edfc268a3f89b440b2.poster.avif?t=1768862859\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/8d3c312f2f2457edfc268a3f89b440b2.webm?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089860/extras/8d3c312f2f2457edfc268a3f89b440b2.mp4?t=1768862859\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us in 'Food Delivery Simulator' and turn every delivery into an adventure. Build your courier career, explore a vibrant city, and rise to the top. Are you ready to become the best courier in town?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
